      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<section class=\"octo-compare-page\">\n  <style>\n    .octo-compare-page {\n      background: #050505;\n      color: #fff;\n      font-family: inherit;\n    }\n\n    .octo-compare-wrap {\n      max-width: 1220px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      padding: 70px 22px 35px;\n    }\n\n    .octo-compare-hero {\n      text-align: center;\n      max-width: 850px;\n      margin: 0 auto 55px;\n    }\n\n    .octo-eyebrow {\n      color: #ff6a00;\n      font-weight: 800;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: .08em;\n      font-size: 13px;\n      margin-bottom: 14px;\n    }\n\n    .octo-compare-hero h1 {\n      font-size: clamp(38px, 6vw, 72px);\n      line-height: .95;\n      margin: 0 0 22px;\n      font-weight: 900;\n    }\n\n    .octo-compare-hero p,\n    .octo-card p,\n    .octo-difference p {\n      color: #d7d7d7;\n      font-size: 18px;\n      line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n\n    .octo-two-col {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n      gap: 28px;\n      margin-bottom: 70px;\n    }\n\n    .octo-card {\n      background: #111;\n      border: 1px solid #262626;\n      border-radius: 28px;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(0,0,0,.35);\n    }\n\n    .octo-card-content {\n      padding: 30px;\n    }\n\n    .octo-card h2 {\n      font-size: 34px;\n      margin: 0 0 12px;\n      line-height: 1;\n    }\n\n    .octo-main-img {\n      width: 100%;\n      aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;\n      object-fit: cover;\n      display: block;\n    }\n\n    .octo-mini-grid {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n      gap: 10px;\n      padding: 0 30px 30px;\n    }\n\n    .octo-mini-grid img {\n      width: 100%;\n      aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;\n      object-fit: cover;\n      border-radius: 16px;\n      display: block;\n    }\n\n    .octo-difference {\n      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111, #070707);\n      border: 1px solid #292929;\n      border-radius: 32px;\n      padding: 42px;\n      margin-bottom: 40px;\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n\n    .octo-difference h2 {\n      font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 52px);\n      margin: 0 0 14px;\n    }\n\n    .octo-difference > p {\n      max-width: 780px;\n      margin: 0 auto 36px;\n    }\n\n    .octo-simple-grid {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n      gap: 22px;\n    }\n\n    .octo-simple-box {\n      background: #050505;\n      border: 1px solid #303030;\n      border-radius: 24px;\n      padding: 28px;\n    }\n\n    .octo-simple-box h3 {\n      margin: 0 0 12px;\n      font-size: 26px;\n      color: #ff6a00;\n    }\n\n    .octo-simple-box p {\n      margin: 0;\n      color: #ddd;\n      line-height: 1.55;\n    }\n\n    @media (max-width: 850px) {\n      .octo-compare-wrap {\n        padding: 48px 18px 25px;\n      }\n\n      .octo-two-col,\n      .octo-simple-grid {\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      }\n\n      .octo-card-content,\n      .octo-mini-grid {\n        padding-left: 22px;\n        padding-right: 22px;\n      }\n\n      .octo-difference {\n        padding: 30px 20px;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <div class=\"octo-compare-wrap\">\n\n    <div class=\"octo-compare-hero\">\n      <div class=\"octo-eyebrow\">Compare Patch Styles</div>\n      <h1>Traditional Custom Patches or 3D Flex?</h1>\n      <p>\n        Both are premium, heat-applied, durable, and made for real-world use.\n        The difference is what you are designing: the patch itself, or the artwork that becomes the patch.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"octo-two-col\">\n\n      <div class=\"octo-card\">\n        <img class=\"octo-main-img\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0834/8562/2516/files/various_patches.png?v=1783361469\" alt=\"Various custom patches\">\n        <div class=\"octo-card-content\">\n          <div class=\"octo-eyebrow\">Custom Patches</div>\n          <h2>Design the Patch</h2>\n          <p>\n            Choose the patch shape, material look, border style, background texture, and dimensional logo details.\n            Your artwork is added onto a finished patch style.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"octo-mini-grid\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0834/8562/2516/files/Iron_Thread.png?v=1783376197\" alt=\"Leather bag with custom patch\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0834/8562/2516/files/MyTimeSports.png?v=1783376196\" alt=\"Hunting gloves with custom patch\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0834/8562/2516/files/WhiteRabbit.png?v=1783376196\" alt=\"Visor with metal-look custom patch\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0834/8562/2516/files/Boar_Fig.png?v=1783376196\" alt=\"Chef coat with custom patch\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"octo-card\">\n        <img class=\"octo-main-img\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0834/8562/2516/files/3D_Flex_various_images.png?v=1783528993\" alt=\"Various 3D Flex examples\">\n        <div class=\"octo-card-content\">\n          <div class=\"octo-eyebrow\">3D Flex</div>\n          <h2>Design the Artwork</h2>\n          <p>\n            Your artwork becomes the patch. Choose which areas are raised, flat, matte, or glossy to create a bold dimensional design.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"octo-mini-grid\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0834/8562/2516/files/3D_Health_Food_Co_Logo_on_Jacket.png?v=1783539578\" alt=\"3D Flex on jacket\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0834/8562/2516/files/3D_Construction_Logo_on_Work_Gloves.png?v=1783539578\" alt=\"3D Flex on work gloves\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0834/8562/2516/files/3D_Lacrosse_Logo_on_Sports_Bag.png?v=1783539577\" alt=\"3D Flex on sports bag\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0834/8562/2516/files/3D_Coffee_Shop_Logo_on_Apron.png?v=1783539578\" alt=\"3D Flex on apron\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"octo-difference\">\n      <h2>The Biggest Difference</h2>\n      <p>\n        Custom Patches start with a patch style. 3D Flex starts with your artwork.\n        Same application. Different design experience. Very different look.\n      </p>\n\n      <div class=\"octo-simple-grid\">\n        <div class=\"octo-simple-box\">\n          <h3>Custom Patches</h3>\n          <p>\n            Your logo sits on a custom-designed patch. You choose the shape, material look, border, and texture first.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"octo-simple-box\">\n          <h3>3D Flex</h3>\n          <p>\n            Your artwork defines the finished shape. Raised areas, flat areas, gloss, and matte effects are built into the design itself.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>",
