px 28px;\n      margin-bottom: 70px;\n    }\n\n    .octo-application h2 {\n      font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 48px);\n      margin: 0 0 14px;\n    }\n\n    .octo-application p {\n      color: #d2d2d2;\n      max-width: 760px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      font-size: 18px;\n      line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n\n    .octo-final-cta {\n      text-align: center;\n      padding: 10px 0 0;\n    }\n\n    .octo-final-cta h2 {\n      font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 58px);\n      margin: 0 0 16px;\n    }\n\n    .octo-final-cta p {\n      color: #d2d2d2;\n      font-size: 18px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      max-width: 720px;\n      line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n\n    @media (max-width: 850px) {\n      .octo-compare-wrap-bottom {\n        padding: 30px 18px 50px;\n      }\n\n      .octo-two-col {\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      }\n\n      .octo-card-content {\n        padding: 24px 22px;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <div class=\"octo-compare-wrap-bottom\">\n\n    <div class=\"octo-table-wrap\">\n      <table class=\"octo-table\">\n        <thead>\n          <tr>\n            <th>Feature</th>\n            <th>Custom Patches</th>\n            <th>3D Flex</th>\n          </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Best way to think about it</td>\n            <td>You are designing a patch.</td>\n            <td>You are designing dimensional artwork.</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Shape</td>\n            <td>Choose a patch shape.</td>\n            <td>The artwork creates the shape.</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Material look</td>\n            <td>Choose faux leather, denim, wood, cork, twill, carbon fiber, and more.</td>\n            <td>No separate material choice. Textures must be part of the artwork.</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Dimension</td>\n            <td>Logo details can be raised, recessed, or flat.</td>\n            <td>Individual parts of the artwork can be raised, flat, matte, or glossy.</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Finish</td>\n            <td>Premium patch finishes with realistic texture and depth.</td>\n            <td>Matte finish with optional gloss effects.</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Best for</td>\n            <td>Classic, premium, traditional patch looks.</td>\n            <td>Bold logos, characters, modern graphics, and dimensional designs.</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Application</td>\n            <td>Heat applied.</td>\n            <td>Heat applied.</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Durability</td>\n            <td>Built for everyday use.</td>\n            <td>Built for everyday use.</td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"octo-section-title\">Which Style Should You Choose?</h2>\n\n    <div class=\"octo-two-col\">\n      <div class=\"octo-card\">\n        <img class=\"octo-main-img\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0834/8562/2516/files/Iron_Thread.png?v=1783376197\" alt=\"Custom patch on bag\">\n        <div class=\"octo-card-content\">\n          <h2>Choose Custom Patches If...</h2>\n          <ul class=\"octo-list\">\n            <li>You want a traditional patch look.</li>\n            <li>You want to choose a patch material, shape, and border.</li>\n            <li>You like faux leather, denim, wood, cork, twill, or stitched styles.</li>\n            <li>You want your logo added onto a premium patch background.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"octo-card\">\n        <img class=\"octo-main-img\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0834/8562/2516/files/3D_Construction_Logo_on_Work_Gloves.png?v=1783539578\" alt=\"3D Flex on work gloves\">\n        <div class=\"octo-card-content\">\n          <h2>Choose 3D Flex If...</h2>\n          <ul class=\"octo-list\">\n            <li>You want your artwork to become the patch.</li>\n            <li>You want to control raised and flat areas inside the design.</li>\n            <li>You want matte and gloss effects in the same piece.</li>\n            <li>You want a modern, dimensional, sculpted look.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"octo-application\">\n      <h2>Same Great Application</h2>\n      <p>\n        Custom Patches and 3D Flex both apply with heat and are built for hats, jackets, bags, uniforms, workwear, and everyday use.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"octo-final-cta\">\n      <h2>Ready to Start Designing?</h2>\n      <p>\n        Pick the style that fits your project. Classic patch or modern 3D artwork. Either way, your brand gets the upgrade.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>",
